HEADWORD: Brinded
<hw>Brin"ded</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. Icel.
<ets>br⟦oum⟧nd⟦omac⟧ttr</ets> brindled, fr. <ets>brandr</ets> brand; and
